title: 【#スバおか】マリオテニスフィーバーで遊ぶしゅばあああああああああああああああああ！！！：Mario Tennis Fever【ホロライブ/大空スバル】
name: Oozora Subaru

entries.text: Yes, hello, sorry for barging in!
By the way, is the audio okay?
Is the sound popping at all?
Did you just wake up? Correct, correct, correct. Hello, freshly awake person.
Yes, so, Nekomata-san is actually using a standing setup today, so let's do this!
Right? Time has stopped. Time has totally stopped, so we can do whatever we want.
Our origin story always begins with tennis.
Yeah, that's true. We have a long history.
Yeah, SubaOka actually started by pulling an all-nighter watching Prince of Tennis, so our tennis history is long.
Well, well, well. So today I want to play some serious tennis, you cool with that?
Yes, yes, of course! You could call this the ancestor of the SubaOka Party.
Well, that's true. While eating pickles.
I want to play while remembering those days of eating pickles and binge-watching Prince of Tennis all night.
Right, along with some slightly fancy bottled apple juice.
Whoa—wait, what was that grape juice called?
Ah, Welch's! Those days of drinking Welch's and eating pickles.
Okay, okay, okay. Closing entries, closing entries!
By the way, apparently there are...
Hey, Nekomata-san, you've played this once before, right?
I only have about three extra characters myself.
For me, Power type is the only choice.
I don't know! I booted it up earlier and...
I don't even know what effect this special racket has!
You look like a banana harvester!
Your harvesting power is too strong!
Also, I forgot to turn off the flowers!
I forgot to turn off the flowers in the commentary!
Ah, I see what you mean.
This guy talks way too much.
Don't take points with body shots!
I'm gonna shave off your HP!
Isn't that banana being too modest?
I can't even move forward anymore!
If I return a shot in the mud, does my HP go down?
This isn't tennis! This isn't tennis!
This is tennis! If I say it's tennis, it's tennis!
Look, my feet are so fast!
I'll shake you left and right!
That movement just now was actually crazy.
The Fever Shot I couldn't use properly...
Bananas are scattered everywhere! It's a greengrocer!
No way! You ate the whole greengrocer inventory!
Oh crap! Don't eat it! Seriously!
Wait, what is this about HP running out?
I think it drops when you take a Special Move... or when you trip...
Or when you take a ball to the face.
No, no, what do you mean HP drops in tennis?!
Well, true. Basically, this isn't normal tennis.
Exactly. Hey, this is open: Waluigi Pinball stage.
There shouldn't be gimmicks there, probably.
Nice. I'll try someone else since it's open.
She said it was hard to use.
Oh crap, Donkey's back is too huge.
He's a Power type, after all.
Wait, the wind is mixing in, so annoying!
I can't see the screen anymore!
Is this like the Blooper in Mario Kart?
Come on, come on, come on!
Ah, crap, if I try to avoid the mud...
I have no choice but to enter the mud.
No, I don't want to go in the mud!
You sound like a fake Ryoma Echizen.
I'll even run through the mud!
It was so loud I didn't notice the flower commentary at all.
I want to try using a cute one.
They say it's a Rosalina meta.
Seems to be Donkey and Rosalina.
What is this Mario Racket anyway?
I don't think it dirties the stage or anything.
I'll go with the Electric Racket.
You're going to become the mama!
Eh, you say stuff like that?
Wait a sec, the floating is crazy!
So the ball curves a lot.
This time for sure, a shot!
If you shoot, return to the center!
Subaru-chan, yours probably curves that much too.
Freeze curves are nasty! If I'm not in the center, I'm in trouble!
No time to even unleash my electricity?!
True! It curves and takes the character with it!
Ah! Darn it! Do I stop moving if I charge? If I spin twice?
Yeah, yeah. If you charge, you stop moving.
No! Ah, seriously, I'm quitting Gachapu (button mashing)!
Can I not win unless I graduate from Gachapu? This.
When you graduate Gachapu, that is when Subaru-chan wins.
It's the racket, surely! The racket!
Want to try the same racket?
Stop, stop! That'll just expose how bad I am!
I'm using a racket Subaru-chan doesn't have.
Hey, what is that? It's huge!
It comes out, the rocket. But maybe Waluigi is better.
Kamek made me suffer recently, brings back memories. Ah, you're playing Mario World.
You were saying something about Fuzzies (Keseran-Pasaran).
Yeah, yeah. I thought it was a Fuzzy.
But apparently it wasn't a Fuzzy.
Turns out it was a Tumbleweed.
I'll flip up the grandma or something.
Wow, two of us doing it is crazy.
Too fast, suddenly there were two.
Where should I stand?! My HP is critical!
I'm going to die! I'm going to die!
There's a Birikyu over here too!
There's one over here too, a Birikyu!
No, no, why do you sound so happy?
The winner will be decided next.
Just now, the ball my ally hit...
It's thumping like crazy, that's nasty, what is this?
No, that's not heart failure, that's Match Point.
This game is interesting, isn't it?
Give me that electric ball thing too!
Want to, want to, want to!
Getting hit by my ally's ball...
It is tennis. This is proof that the tennis we loved was always like this.
True. The tennis we loved was always like this, forever.
That's right. Okay, sent the invite.
Never played it, not at all.
But Nekomata-san, you're good at Mario Tennis, seriously.
Really, you think? I don't feel like I'm good at it though.
What kind of match is next?
Special Game Match. Apparently, it's chaotic.
Is there anything more chaotic than what we just did?
That already didn't seem like tennis.
Look, just because you add "Fever," doesn't mean you can do whatever.
There are 5 rules. Want to go from the top? Ring Shot.
Ah, sure. But Ring Shot is just spamming, right?
Eh, want to do this one?
"Feed balls to the Piranha Plants on the opponent's court."
What is this? What does that mean? Okay.
I don't know, absolutely no idea.
Koopa Troopa (Nokonoko)... I can change colors, nice.
We can't choose rackets? Looks like it.
Hey, I can't return from my turtle form!
Well, you are a turtle, always.
I am a turtle, but... I'm stuck in my shell and can't change back!
Ah, you mean the filling won't come out?
Yeah, yeah, the filling won't come out!
Maybe if you stop, it comes out?
Wait, this is a high-level character!
Crap! Only my court is getting wider!
But if it's wide, there's more area to cover.
Isn't it one of those things?
Like if it gets too wide, you instant death?
If it all becomes green, it's instant death!
To begin with, Turtle is hard?
To begin with, Turtle is hard.
But my Fever is charged too!
Power is strong with this one.
This game is won by whoever has the bigger physique.
What, what? It disappeared, it disappeared!
What is this? What is this?
If you hit the round thing with the ball...
It seems to go "Gon gon gon".
I can't control it that well!
Wait, it turned into your ball.
You wait, they're going in like crazy!
If we get Fever like 3 times...
It seems the person who gets the 3rd one starts the Pinball.
Ah, I see. I didn't know.
That's just the kind of stage it is.
I see. Yeah, lots of stuff. Let's try Ring Shot too.
Seriously, it got stuck and couldn't get out, thought it was over. No~ Pon pon pon pon pon.
Oh oh oh oh! This has been around since the old days, right? Since 64? Oh, really? Yeah, I think so.
Wait! I might be good at this!
Ball coming from the side is nasty.
But this is that kind of game.
Better to stay further back for this.
Give me the ball, ball, ball!
Scary. Me too. Me too tennis. Me too push. Me too waaaa!
Want to play, want to play!
"Hit the glowing floor panels on the opponent's court to get one Fever Shot." Apparently.
I see. Seems like control is important again.
It's technique after all. I'll go with Peach.
I'm always Peach, no matter the era.
Ah, does this not come out?
Poi poi, do this and Fever charges.
Peach, you're a bit slow on foot.
Don't mess up because of Peach!
Peach-san is always trying her best!
It stops being a Normal Racket, probably.
I think if you do a Special Move like normal it should work.
Hurry up and let me use Donkey Kong!
This isn't a game about looks!
It's a game of strength! I want to do that too! That too!
Umm, "Enter the World of Wonder with Wonder Flower."
-- Looks like you made something! -- Eh, San-Can looks crazy.
-- To the World of Wonder. -- What's that?
It's where the commentary flower is from.
-- Eh, there's a seed thing! -- Eh?
-- Should we grab that? Bottom left or right, there's a seed? -- Ah, nice!
Subaru-chan, you should definitely play Wonder.
We played Wonder once for Calli-ope.
That's pretty much a god game.
At that time I hadn't played action games yet.
Ah, if you win you get it? Wonder Seed.
Probably if we collect them all...
We can go to the World of Wonder.
Let's hit the Wonder Seed with the ball.
Eh, is this a rhythm game?
Ah, if you go where the spotlight hits, you can shoot.
Okay, okay, this isn't necessarily the Wonder World yet.
Don't we have to collect them all?
I understand now! What this tennis thing is!
If Wonder Seeds fill up, it ends.
For Subaru, Pinball and Ring Shot.
Let's do Pinball, one more time.
We can also remake the room and play normally.
You fit right into Pinball because you have the same physique.
Dangerous, almost got stuck in the Pinball.
Is it dangerous to get close to the Pinball?
One more and Fever starts, right?
Which ball is it?! Which ball, where?!
What to do? Remake room and play normal?
Let's do that last one, the 1000 points one.
Amazing, being toyed with by Pinball right now.
Eh, how do you shoot a low ball?
Probably Y, Y might be strongest for this rule.
Right? Y is strong. It's a Y-Game.
My ball, my ball, my ball, my ball!
No, raise the chance with that!
Ball where, ball where, ball where!
Ball where, ball where, ball where, ball where!
This is already becoming a disaster.
You said "We can only do 1 hour today~".
If it wasn't 1 hour, our stamina would run out!
I didn't think it was such an intense game!
No, Mario Tennis is hell if you go over an hour.
Because last time I played with Nekomata-san...
In Mario Tennis 64 or something, the enemy was super strong.
Ah right, we played Doubles together.
Right, right. I only remembered that feeling.
I didn't think it would be such a party game!
The amount of info is crazy.
It turned into something like this?
Impossible to play without making noise.
We only have about 10 minutes left.
So, absolutely no making noise Mario Tennis.
Wait, does this mean there's a punishment game?
We're too used to hell already.
Exactly, I don't really feel "punishment" anymore. What punishment game is there?
Gotta be this. Alright, "No Laughing, No Noise Mario Tennis", Start.
Start. Look, my racket is missing a piece.
Not a fart! The Hey is too loud.
This just becomes a normal serious match.
I always wonder what a Tie-Break is.
Means you can do what Kaidoh does.
As expected, laughing makes you more alive.
Right? If they steal our laughter, we don't know what to do!
Bad bad bad bad! Soul, soul!
Boomerang Snake is crazy! Coming from outside the frame!
Do I have to guess the 50/50?
Hey, it looks like it'll curve.
Crap, I have too few rackets.
I'm going for the finish first!
Crap, crap! My field is already...
Nekomata-san, you should become a tennis player.
No, it's because I'm scared of the banana that I can't play tennis!
I'll charge in assuming the banana doesn't exist.
I see. That might actually be important.
Exactly, being scared of this banana is the problem!
Do it! It became super strong after turning into a banana!
Maybe you should fear it? Banana.
I got it. I'll step on it first.
I'm watching Harry Potter after this.
The Greengrocer is going to see Harry Potter after this.
Look, someone is setting the Greengrocer on fire!
Greengrocer, don't cut the Love Smash!
But by the time you understand, you'll be off to Harry Potter.
Right, I'm going to Harry Potter.
Can't win being so far back!
Shut up, if I go forward I burst into flames!
If you don't need to be forward...
This is the power of the Greengrocer.
Don't know. It becomes like this...
When you take one from a tie.
Tiger Break! Early Departure (Sousou) Tiger Break!
I'll do an Early Departure (Sousou) Frieren.
Is this okay? Doing an Early Departure Frieren?
Should I give a contact Frieren?
I'll let them know just in case.
If you die in singles, what happens?
Do you get slower feet or something?
You went and shaved your own life!
A battle I cannot lose is right here.
I can't afford to go easy.
Which way, which way, which way, which way!
No, this isn't the time for that!
Good feel! It's gonna bound high!
Stop lying! I'll close it out!
Ranked Match, Ranked Match is serious business.
Thank you very much for today.
Thank you very much for today.
I didn't expect the Greengrocer to be good. Freeze Racket.
Uwa, this one? Birikyu. DD. Uwaa, Curve Racket, Ink Racket.
Yes, so, thank you for today.
Umm, tomorrow is a day off.
Friday is normal... Friday, Saturday, Sunday are normal, so...
Alright everyone, thank you for today!
Thank you for watching NEXT STREAM.
